{"tid":828904,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭 : 社會朝更團結包容方向前進","createTime":"2018-09-20T04:26:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-21T02:15:07.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"630a50ffdea6d30a9e9b89f1f602c1252ecb2e4b","tid":828904,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T04:26:44.000Z","msg":"行政長官林鄭月娥出席一個慈善論壇時表示，指本港的慈善服務歷史悠久，慈善機構數目由2006年的4400間，今年已倍增至接近9000間，社會正朝着更包容、更具同情心，以及更團結的方向前進。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥指出，特區政府多年來增加資源致力扶貧，並成立基金資助有意投身慈善的初創企業家，過去3年已向140個項目資助超過1.2億元。<br />\n<br />\n她又說，慈善服務不能只靠政府，亦要有賴商界的協助，通過創新的做法，改善整體社會的生活質素。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/1949236/%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%3A%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%9C%9D%E6%9B%B4%E5%9C%98%E7%B5%90%E5%8C%85%E5%AE%B9%E6%96%B9%E5%90%91%E5%89%8D%E9%80%B2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F1949236%2F%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD%253A%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%259C%259D%25E6%259B%25B4%25E5%259C%2598%25E7%25B5%2590%25E5%258C%2585%25E5%25AE%25B9%25E6%2596%25B9%25E5%2590%2591%25E5%2589%258D%25E9%2580%25B2&d=hLOWhBhG0hlTLctC6GWcNV0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=135af00a\" target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/1949236/%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%3A%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%9C%9D%E6%9B%B4%E5%9C%98%E7%B5%90%E5%8C%85%E5%AE%B9%E6%96%B9%E5%90%91%E5%89%8D%E9%80%B2</a>"},{"pid":"6ac4ca43630c19576a179e62f07ac158a6535967","tid":828904,"uid":66044,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T04:32:44.000Z","msg":"團你老母 包你老母咩 難聽過粗口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d21ae8ed8d502151443443e7eb8aa901fb4b350c","tid":828904,"uid":19978,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T04:36:45.000Z","msg":"主語放錯左，係啲老闆更團結咁恰打工仔"},{"pid":"75c2cf6639d0d4bb79a760fcd4d8483be16c945b","tid":828904,"uid":108347,"li